INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (14,'James Bond Cashmere-Lined Leather Gloves - By N.Peal','Crafted from supple leather and lined with luxurious cashmere, the James Bond Cashmere-lined Leather Gloves - On Her Majesty\'s Secret Service Edition - By N.Peal are inspired by ones worn as 007 skis down Piz Gloria in the 1969 film.\r\n\r\nPart of the limited edition 007 Cashmere Collection created by British cashmere experts N.Peal, the design is made in England by glove specialists Dents. Established in 1777, Dents gloves have appeared in many Bond films over the years, including Skyfall(2012) and Spectre (2015).\r\n\r\nBackstory. When 007 escapes Blofeld\'s mountain-top lair he embarks on a daring Alpine chase, evading his assassins dressed in a statement blue ski suit with black gloves and accessories. \r\n\r\nDetails. These gloves have a soft leather outer with an opulent cashmere lining. A distinctive 007-etched metal popper fastening secures the fit at the wrists, while stitching reinforces strength and shape. The leather will flex with movement and mould to your hand shape, providing years of wear, while the cashmere inner ensures comfort and superb temperature control.\r\n\r\nPerfectly finished with an N.Peal 007 stitched label and exclusive swing ticket.\r\n\r\nCare. If your gloves get wet, allow them to dry naturally. Heavy soiling can be taken care of by a specialised leather dry cleaner, but if the soiling is light and not dried in, you can try the following:\r\n\r\nPrepare a hand hot solution of soft soap flakes such as \"Lux\"\r\nGently sponge down the outside leather of the gloves with this solution\r\nTry not to saturate the leather and dab off any excess wetness with a clean dry cloth\r\nAllow the gloves to dry naturally \r\nAs the gloves are drying, put them on your hands several times - this will help to stretch the leather and restore their shape \r\nIf you decide to use a proprietary leather cleaner or conditioner, please read the product instructions carefully and be sure the product you are using is suitable for your glove leather.',159,'1695692543973.webp',1),(15,'Scalextric James Bond DB5 Slot Car - Goldfinger Edition','Available to pre-order, shipping Summer 2023.\r\n\r\nThe Scalextric James Bond DB5 Slot Car is based on the model driven by 007 in Goldfinger (1964). \r\n\r\nBackstory. When 007 first took control of the DB5 in Goldfinger (1964) it redefined the action movie forever, setting a standard for everything that came afterwards. Over the decades that have followed, Bond\'s association with Aston Martin has only grown stronger. Bond and the DB5 are the perfect match: understated, stylish and powerful. The DB5 features in seven 007 films, from 1964’s Goldfinger,to Thunderball, GoldenEye, Tomorrow Never Dies, Casino Royale, Skyfall, Spectre and No Time To Die.\r\n\r\nDetails. A replica of the Aston Martin DB5 in 1:32 scale. The slot car has rubber tyres, easy change pick-ups, high detail Magnatraction and xenon-effect headlights. It is also digital plug ready - digital plug not included. Suitable for ages 5+.   \r\n                             \r\n            \r\n                             \r\n            ',54,'1696164395903.webp',5),(16,'James Bond 007 Spymaster Duo Fountain Pen - By Montegrappa','Introducing the James Bond 007 Spymaster Duo Fountain Pen by Montegrappa. Inspired by 007, this collectors\' edition writing instrument is fitting companion for any assignment. In the best traditions of James Bond gadgetry, the 007 Spymaster Duo has hidden secrets and is stylishly handmade from precious materials in a numbered edition of just 380 pieces. \r\n\r\nDetails.The pen is constructed from high-strength machined steel and aluminium. Its false upper barrel conceals a pair of special edition 007 cufflinks which can be\r\naccessed via a special locking mechanism and dummy blind cap. The pen has a reference-level 8mm nib in 18K gold, custom-engraved with the James Bond 60th Anniversary logo, and is engraved with its individual number on the steel grip.Features include the advanced Swift-Shot filling – an innovation which makes pioneering use of Montegrappa’s coveted Power-Push mechanism, The Swift-shot filling offers writers remote filling using high-capacity 007 \'bullet\' brass ink cartridges. A pair of cartridges is supplied together with an alloy/steel reloading pipette that uses Power-push hydraulic action to fill without spills. Filled cartridges are inserted into the writing block before reaffixing the barrel. \r\n\r\nThe pen features rifling on the cap and upper barrel which echoes the iconic, gun-barrel title sequence. The lower barrel is made of blackened alloy with a knurled, pistol-grip finish. Additional product markings include the 007 logo on the blind cap, cufflinks and a chevron pocket-clip, and the Bond family crest foil-stamped onto a companion journal. The pen and Swift-Shot accessories are housed in a custom travel case with secret compartments and a journal and two bottles of 007-branded ink.\r\n\r\nDimensions. L16.20cm, D1.85cm\r\n\r\nThe makers. Montegrappa has been manufacturing the world’s most magical pens in the same artisanal factory for more than a century. Combining luxurious materials, high craftsmanship and unrivalled writing pleasure, the independent maker’s quality and individualist flair make it a firm favourite of dignitaries, creatives and collectors. All Montegrappa writing instruments are made at the company’s headquarters beneath Monte Grappa in Bassano del Grappa, Italy\r\n                             \r\n            ',4495,'1695692815329.webp',1),(17,'James Bond Honey Ryder 1OZ Silver Minted Mini Coin - By The Perth Mint','              \r\n                      Introducing the James Bond 1oz Silver Minted Mini Coin - Numbered Edition - By The Perth Mint, the second in a series of 007 precious chibi character coins.\r\n\r\nBrought to the big screen in 1962\'s Dr. No, Ursula Andress made waves as the fictional shell diver Honey Ryder, becoming one of the most iconic characters of the James Bond franchise.\r\n\r\nStruck by The Perth Mint from 1oz of 99.99% pure silver, this coin is issued as legal tender under the authority of the Government of Tuvalu. The Perth Mint will release no more than 2,500 of the coins.\r\n\r\nBackstory. The Minted Minis are inspired by Japanese chibi and represents all the creative and technical processes that have been associated with The Perth Mint for more than 100 years. The result is a fun, intricate character presented in the form of a uniquely shaped silver coin. Chibi is a Japanese term describing a specific style of caricature where characters are drawn in an exaggerated way, very much inspired by Japanese anime.\r\n\r\nDetails. The reverse of the character-shaped coin portrays a stylised colour representation of Honey in her iconic white bikini with a knife belt and shell. The obverse of the coin bears the Ian Rank-Broadley effigy of Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth II supplemented with the dates of her reign ‘1952-2022’, as well as the coin’s weight, purity, monetary denomination and 2023 year date. Each coin is presented in a clear acrylic case, allowing both sides of the coin to be displayed standing up, and is accompanied by a numbered Certificate of Authenticity. \r\n\r\nDimensions. H37mm, W30mm, D6.50mm, weight 31.107g\r\n\r\nThe makers. The Perth Mint is Australia\'s official bullion mint and is wholly owned by the Government of Western Australia. The mint manufactures and distributes platinum, silver and gold coins for collectors and customers worldwide. \r\n                             \r\n            \r\n                             \r\n            ',135,'1695692980549.webp',3),(18,'James Bond Zippo Lighter - You Only Live Twice Red Edition','lease note. This item can only be shipped within the UK.\r\n\r\nThe legacy of the iconic James Bond films is honored with this classic windproof Zippo lighter decorated with a You Only Live Twice design.\r\n\r\nBackstory. Bond travels incognito to Japan to investigate the hijacking of American and Russian spacecraft. Together with Tiger Tanaka and Aki of the Japanese Secret Service, Bond traces a supply of liquid oxygen to a southern Japanese island. He goes undercover and discovers that SPECTRE, commanded by Ernst Stavro Blofeld, have a secret rocket complex hidden inside a volcano.\r\n\r\nDetails. The James Bond Zippo Lighter - You Only Live Twice Red Edition is a bold design with an iconic Sean Connery poster illustration. The classic Zippo hinged case has a refillable construction to give a lifetime of use. Sold unfilled and with a Zippo lifetime guarantee. Presented in a 007 Zippo gift box.\r\n\r\nFeatures.\r\n\r\nDurable metal outer case\r\nRefillable\r\nHinged lid\r\nWindproof\r\nMade in the USA\r\nOfficially licensed Zippo product\r\nLifetime guarantee \r\nLighters are unable to be delivered outside of the UK due to legal shipping restrictions. Any orders will automatically be cancelled.\r\n\r\n                            \r\n            ',79,'1695693036508.webp',1),(19,'Polo black spectre symbol - Dr. No Edition - By Orlebar Brown','Step into the shadows.\r\n\r\nThe James Bond SPECTRE Symbol Embroidered Polo Shirt is a premium organic cotton two button design with the SPECTRE symbol embroidered in subtle grey thread.\r\n\r\nBackstory. Representing the Special Executive for Counter-intelligence, Terrorism, Revenge and Extortion, the iconic SPECTRE organisation mark first appeared in the film From Russia With Love in 1963 and was updated for Spectre in 2015. \r\n\r\nDetails. This premium pique polo is 100% organic ring-spun cotton, 230gsm.\r\n\r\nSizes.  S 36/38\" M 38/40\" L 41/43\" XL 43/45\" 2XL 46/47\" 3XL 48/50\"',30,'1696160206134.webp',2),(20,'James Bond BMW R1200C Model Bike - Tomorrow Never Dies Edition - By Motormax','              \r\n                      The James Bond BMW R1200C Model Bike - Tomorrow Never Dies Edition - By Motormax isa die-cast replica of the bikeused in the film\'s Ho Chi Minh City scenes.\r\n\r\nBackstory. In this scene, Bond and Wai Lin ride the cruiser to make a 44-foot leap across two rooftops over the blades of a pursuing helicopter, and later slide under it. \r\n\r\nDetails.A die-cast model made in perfect scale with rubber tyres and moving wheels. The doors, boot and bonnet open to reveala meticulously detailed interior. Presented in a full-colour diorama box.\r\n\r\nDimensions.L130mm\r\n\r\nThe makers.For over two decades, Motormax has specialised in constructing highly detailed and specialised collectible replicas of officially licensed cars, planes and other vehicles.\r\n                             \r\n            ',20,'1696165753529.webp',5),(21,'James Bond 1OZ Silver Minted Mini Coin - By The Perth Mint','Global exclusive. Introducing the James Bond 1oz Silver Minted Mini Coin - Numbered Edition - By The Perth Mint, the first in a series of 007 precious chibi character coins.\r\n\r\nStruck by The Perth Mint from 1oz of 99.99% pure silver, this coin is issued as legal tender under the authority of the Government of Tuvalu. The Perth Mint will release no more than 2,500 of the coins.\r\n\r\nBackstory. The Minted Minis are inspired by Japanese chibi and represents all the creative and technical processes that have been associated with The Perth Mint for more than 100 years. The result is a fun, intricate character presented in the form of a uniquely shaped silver coin. Chibi is a Japanese term describing a specific style of caricature where characters are drawn in an exaggerated way, very much inspired by Japanese anime.\r\n\r\nDetails. The reverse of the character-shaped coin portrays a stylised colour representation of James Bond in his iconic white dinner jacket with a martini. The obverse of the coin bears the Ian Rank-Broadley effigy of Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth II supplemented with the dates of her reign ‘1952-2022’, as well as the coin’s weight, purity, monetary denomination and 2023 year date. Each coin is presented in a clear acrylic case, allowing both sides of the coin to be displayed standing up, and is accompanied by a numbered Certificate of Authenticity. \r\n\r\nDimensions. H37mm, W30mm, D6.50mm, weight 31.107g\r\n\r\nThe makers. The Perth Mint is Australia\'s official bullion mint and is wholly owned by the Government of Western Australia. The mint manufactures and distributes platinum, silver and gold coins for collectors and customers worldwide. ',135,'1696166122652.webp',3),(22,'James Bond 007 Zippo Lighter - Black Case With Gold Logo','lease note, this item can only be shipped within the UK.\r\n\r\nThe legacy of the iconic James Bond films is honored with this classic windproof Zippo lighter.\r\n\r\nDetails. The James Bond 007 Zippo Lighter - Black Case With Gold Logo is a sleek and timeless design presented in a 007 Zippo gift box.\r\n\r\nGenuine Zippo windproof lighter with distinctive Zippo \"click\"\r\nWindproof design works virtually anywhere\r\nRefillable for a lifetime of use\r\nMade in USA\r\nLifetime guarantee that \"it works or we fix it free™\"\r\nFuel: Zippo premium lighter fuel (sold separately)\r\nLighters are unable to be delivered outside of the UK due to legal shipping restrictions. Any orders will automatically be cancelled.           ',50,'1696167124397.webp',1),(23,'James Bond Dove Cufflinks - For Your Eyes Only Edition','A 007Store exclusive.  \r\n\r\nThe James Bond For Your Eyes OnlyDove Cufflinks are inspired by cufflinks worn by Greek smuggler Milos Columbo in the 1981 film. \r\n\r\nBackstory. Known in the Greek underworld as \"The Dove,\" Columbo helps Bond to retrieve the ATAC device from his former partner and bitter enemy Aristotle Kristatos.\r\n\r\nDetails. A pair of high quality cufflinks featuring an enamel stamped circular face decorated with a white dove and blue surround within gold finish bronze. The cufflinks are presented in a black 007 gift box.',20,'1696177270957.webp',3),(24,'James Bond Spectre Bone Chine Mug','The James Bond Spectre Bone China Mug features a image of Bond in undercover stealth mode from the film\'s poster.\r\n\r\nDetails. The mug comes a special presentation box making it an ideal gift for any 007 fan.            ',13,'1696177503809.webp',3),(25,'James Bond 007 British Milk Chocolate Bar - By Et Walker','              \r\n                                    \r\n                      Exuding sartorial British style, we celebrate the partnership of two iconic brands - James Bond and Bond Street\'s Charbonnel et Walker chocolate - with a delicious James Bond 007 British Milk Chocolate Bar in dashing union jack livery.\r\n\r\nBackstory. Part of Charbonnel et Walker\'s British butler bar series, this chunky size is inspired by the chocolate bars traditionally found in the pantries and kitchen store cupboards of fine houses. \r\n\r\nDetails. The 80g/2.8oz bar is made up of three chunky fingers of fine British milk chocolate, within a sealed airtight paper wrapper. This is presented in a union jack rigid card case complete with embossed 007 and Charbonnel et Walker gold foil detailing.\r\n\r\nDimensions. Chocolate bar is W10cm, H10cm, D1cm, 8g / 2.08oz\r\n\r\nIngredients.Sugar, cocoa butter, whole milk powder, cocoa mass, emulsifier (soya lecithin), natural vanilla flavouring. Milk chocolate contains cocoa solids 33.5% minimum; milk solids 20.5% min. Allergens. Milk, soya. May also contain traces of nuts and gluten.\r\n\r\nThe maker. Founded in 1875, Charbonnel et Walker is one of Britain’s first and finest chocolatiers. Their original shop opened at 173 New Bond Street in Mayfair and has remained in Bond Street ever since - now housed in one of London’s most elegant arcades, the Royal Arcade on Old Bond Street. The company is endorsed by the Royal Warrant as one of the few chocolatiers to Her Majesty The Queen.            \r\n                             \r\n            \r\n                             \r\n            ',7,'1696177698737.jpg',3),(26,'James Bond 007 Leather Circuit Portfolio Case - By Connolly','Introducing the James Bond 007 Leather Circuit Portfolio Case by Connolly, released as a limited edition to celebrate 60 years of James Bond. Connolly’s collaboration with 007 includes a series of timeless leather pieces created in the same Connolly Vaumol leather that has graced the interior of James Bond’s iconic Aston Martin DB5 since Goldfinger in 1964. \r\n\r\nDetails. The iconic Connolly circuit pouch, inspired by racing’s checkered flag, has been reimagined for Bond. This is the perfect place to store a laptop or papers on the move. The understated case has contrasting grained and smooth leather finish on the outside and a padded leather lining inside, finished with a zip closure and interior 007 x Connolly silver foil hallmark - a subtle nod to the original DB5 registration plate.\r\n\r\nAbout Connolly Vaumol leather. Connolly Vaumol leather has been used through history due to its unique patina, aroma and natural grain. From the early days of the motor industry, the leather has covered the interiors of all the Grand Marques, including Rolls Royce, Bentley, Ferrari, Aston Martin and Jaguar. Iconic luxury ocean liners and public buildings around the world, including London’s House of Lords and House of Commons, have also used Connolly Vaumol for their interiors because of its distinctive quality.            ',525,'1696177970944.webp',1),(27,'James Bond Aston Martin V8 Car Keyring','A celebration of the 007 x Aston Martin partnership, this James Bond Aston Martin V8 Car keyring features a polished metal 3D replica of 007\'s classic British saloon.\r\n\r\nBackstory. No Time To Die features a Aston Martin V8 Saloon, similar to the one first seen in 1987’s The Living Daylights. Launched a decade before Timothy Dalton’s Bond debut, the V8 Saloon was both the fastest four-seat production car of its day and Britain’s first true ‘supercar ’.\r\n\r\nDetails. The keyring is crafted from die cast zinc alloy, with a polished silver finish and presented in a black gift box featuring the iconic 007 and Aston Martin logos.\r\n\r\nDimensions. Car is 46mm long            ',18,'1696178111841.jpg',7),(28,'The James Bond Andrea Panama Hat - Special Edition - By Lock & Co.','              \r\n                      Introducing the James Bond Andrea Panama Hat part of the 007 x Lock & Co. limited edition collection.  \r\nA stylish new take on Andrea Anders’ straw panama worn in The Man With The Golden Gun. Ideal for summertime, the design looks as much at home on the beach as at the smartest of special occasion events. Each piece is handwoven and of the finest quality.\r\n\r\n60 years of James Bond style combines with Lock & Co.\'s 346 year hat-making heritage, cementing a long-standing relationship between the two British brands. Designs are inspired by the past and present, referencing archive hats from the series.\r\n\r\nDetails. An elegant and lightweight women’s panama handmade from 100% handwoven Toquilla straw with a wide brim and square crown. This exquisitely finished piece is the ultimate accessory and is finished with an internal sweatband in grosgrain. Made in a limited series, the collector\'s piece is crafted by hand in the traditional way using historic millinery techniques. Presented in a signature Lock & Co. hat box. \r\n\r\nDimensions.Crown H10cm, brim W11.5cm\r\n\r\nSize guide. To find your size, measure by placing a soft tape measure around your head, positioned mid-forehead and just above the ears. Find the corresponding size in cm or inches on the hat size chart in our image gallery\r\n\r\nCare. To clean, steam and brush with a hard bristle hat brush or clean pencil rubber to remove dust and dirt, brushing the hat using short strokes, following the natural direction of the weave. Alternatively, use a soft nailbrush and a little soapy water. Avoid wearing in the rain. If it gets wet, dry using a clean, absorbent cloth or sponge. Stored in a hat box, away from direct sunlight.\r\n\r\nThe makers. Established in 1676, Lock & Co. is the oldest hat shop in the world, the oldest shop in London and one of the oldest family-owned businesses still in existence. No matter the customer, what everyone has come to expect from Lock & Co. is the best: the best designs, the best fabrics, the best service. Their designs have graced the heads of some of the greatest figures in history from Admiral Lord Nelson, Sir Winston Churchill and Oscar Wilde, to David Beckham, Benedict Cumberbatch and Kate Moss. Founded by James Lock, the company is now run by the 7th generation of the family from the shop at No. 6 St. James’s Street, London and holds two Royal Warrants. \r\n                             \r\n            ',1095,'1696178338436.webp',2),(29,'James Bond Womens\'s V Neck Cashmere Sweater - By N. Peal','              \r\n                                  \r\n                             \r\n            ',245,'1696178622245.webp',2),(30,'James Bond Zig Zag Silk Tie - Special Edition - By Turnbull & Asser','A sartorial silk tie created exclusively by Royal Warrant holders Turnbull & Asser for The World Is Not Enough (1999). Turnbull & Asser worked closely with the film\'s costume designer and star to create a sleek, elegant look befitting a stylish 00 agent. \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nBackstory. Designed specially for Pierce Brosnan, the James Bond Zig Zag Silk Tie The World Is Not Enough Edition By Turnbull & Asser has been meticulously recreated using the original patterns and receipts from the Bond and Turnbull & Asser Archives.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nDetails. The silk for this English-made tie is woven in a jacquard design in a deep blue and bronze zig zag pattern with a 3D sense of depth. The tie is tipped in matching silk and lined in a wool blend. All Turnbull & Asser silk ties are hand-sewn in Kent by a team of artisans with centuries of combined experience. The silk used is woven in Suffolk using techniques dating back hundreds of years. The blade of each design features a unique hidden \'loop\' made from strongest-ever bonded thread, which allows the tie to ruche and relax back into place after wearing.\r\n\r\nDimensions. 9.5cm wide\r\n\r\nThe maker. Founded in 1885, Turnbull & Asser is a British shirtmaker and Royal Warrant holder with its flagship store on Jermyn Street, London. Creating luxurious shirts and ties in their English workrooms, the company pride themselves on retaining talented craftspeople with traditional skills. Turnbull & Asser make ready-to-wear, Made to Measure and Bespoke pieces for individuals that appreciate superior quality and craftsmanship.            ',225,'1696178991844.webp',2),(33,'James Bond 007 Personalized Leather - Covered Poker Set','Exclusive to 007Store. The James Bond  007 Personalised Leather-covered Poker Set is a made-to-order item and will take 5-7 working days to produce.\r\n\r\nReady to emboss with a name or initials.\r\n\r\nThe perfect gift. Played by Bond throughout the film series, poker has always been part of the 007 games collection. This sophisticated leather-encased set captures the essence of the classic games evening, while colourful pieces add a stylish feel to proceedings. \r\n\r\nDetails. This is a tabletop game set designed to be displayed. The padded wooden case is covered with softly milled pebble-grained leather and has a compartmentalised interior lined with red velvet. The magnetic lid features a gold 007 logo and hand embossed personalisation. Each set contains two packs of poker-size playing cards, 200 14g poker chips in sets of 25 per colour, two marbled chips for blinds and 4 solid brass dice. \r\n\r\nPersonalise me. Choose up to 6 characters to handprint on the outer case in gold lettering. \r\n\r\nDimensions.  Case L28cm, W20cm H6cm. Chips D40mm',395,'1696773488638.jpg',7),(39,'James Bond Diamonds Are Forever 2OZ Gold Coin - 50TH Anniversary Edition - By The Perth Mint','This very special coin is handmade to order and takes six to eight weeks to make and ship.  A stand-out precious coin for any collector or Bond fan. The Perth Mint celebrates 50 years since the release of Diamonds Are Forever with the James Bond Diamonds Are Forever Diamond-studded 2oz Gold Coin. Struck by The Perth Mint from 2oz of 99.99% pure gold with two hand set white diamonds, made to order in a maximum mintage of 70. Backstory. In the film Bond tracks, SPECTRE boss Blofeld to the US where he discovers his evil nemesis is stockpiling diamonds to power a space-based laser weapon. 007 must neutralise the satellite and prevent SPECTRE from carrying out its threat to global stability. . The coin is made from 2oz of 99.99% pure gold with two hand placed white diamonds, each weighing 0.08ct. The coin is embellished with the Bond family crest and motto along with the number 50. It is presented in a limited edition wooden display box with gold metal hinges, accompanied by a certificate of authenticity. Each coin is made to order in a maximum mintage of 70 and is issued as legal tender under the authority of the Government of Tuvalu. The makers. The Perth Mint is the official mint of Australia and is wholly owned by the Government of Western Australia. The mint manufactures and distributes platinum, silver and gold coins for collectors and customers worldwide. Please note: We recommend keeping your coin within its protective display housing at all times. If touched or left exposed to the air, the freshly minted precious metal will react to atmospheric dust and moisture, as well as oils and acids in the skin, leaving marks that cannot be removed. We cannot be held responsible if this happens. If you do choose to handle your coin, always wear gloves and hold it by its edges.',6950,'1697324732405.jpg',5),(40,'James Bond Teddy Bear - By Steiff','              \r\n                      Introducing the plush James Bond Teddy bear by Steiff. Ideal for all ages, this is a cuddly cousin to the limited edition collector\'s bear.  \r\n\r\nDetails. The bear is made from soft blond, white and black textured plush fabrics, which are fashioned into a stylish evening suit and accessorised with a silky black bow tie. He is part-pellet filled, for a soft and cuddly feel, is fully jointed and has the \"007\" logo embroidered onto his foot in gunmetal grey thread. \r\n\r\nHe features a yellow tag Steiff button in his ear, five swivel joints, so that you can move his arms, legs and head, along with safety eyes. \r\n\r\nDimensions. H30cm\r\n\r\nCare. Machine washable on a gentle cycle.\r\n\r\nAbout the maker.Founded in 1880, Steiff invented the Teddy bear in 1902. This was the world\'s first bear with moveable arms and legs and is the basis of the bear today. Every single part of a Steiff bear continues to be sewn by hand and the Company remain in their original buildings in Germany. Every Steiff Teddy bear proudly wears a button in ear (Knopf Im Orh) as a distinguishing mark, ensuring its authenticity.\r\n                             \r\n            ',89,'1697324973371.webp',5),(41,'James Bond Daniel Craig Autographed Print - Skyfall Roof Numbered Edition','Introducing the James Bond Daniel Craig Autographed Print - Skyfall Rooftop Numbered Edition, a one-of-a-kind collector\'s piece, released in an edition of 125.\r\n\r\nBackstory. Skyfall was released in 2012 to worldwide acclaim not only because it represented the third and perhaps most intriguing film in the Daniel Craig James Bond cinematic universe, but because it coincided with the 50th anniversary of the original Bond film, Dr. No. The reviews were overwhelmingly positive, and the film became the seventh-highest grossing film of all time - the 14th film to surpass the $1 billion threshold in gross sales. Skyfall received two Academy Awards, two BAFTA Awards and two Grammy Awards.\r\n\r\nDetails. This unframed photographic print shows Bond at the end of the film on the London rooftop, and features Daniel Craig\'s autograph in black pen with a unique series number on the lower right corner. His signature is deemed authentic by virtue of Upper Deck Authenticated’s Five-Step Process.\r\n\r\nAuthentication. First, an Upper Deck representative witnesses each autograph signed. A record of the autograph and associated piece of memorabilia is signed by both the star and an Upper Deck official and is then stored securely in a permanent file. An Upper Deck Authenticated serial numbered hologram is affixed to each signed piece of memorabilia. A certificate of authenticity is assigned to each piece of memorabilia and includes a matching hologram to the one affixed to the autographed item. Every piece of signed memorabilia is packaged with a registration card. The owner has the opportunity to register the item with Upper Deck Authenticated. If for some reason the item is sold or transferred to a new owner, a full detailed record of the item\'s history is readily available.\r\n\r\nDimensions. Print W24”, H20” ',1455,'1697325243855.webp',5),(42,'Eva Green Studio Stamped Print - By Greg Williams Photography','              \r\n                                    \r\n                      Introducing a series of limited edition collectors prints by acclaimed photographer Greg Williams.\r\n\r\nNote.  These studio prints are printed to order, please allow 2 weeks for shipping.\r\n\r\nCelebrating the release of No Time To Die, Daniel Craig’s fifth and final film as James Bond, Greg Williams Photography has released a set of limited edition prints - available to own for the first time. Spanning Daniel Craig’s tenure as James Bond, the set of twenty-five black and white photographs give a unique insight into the creation of the iconic films. The images feature Daniel in his role as James Bond, alongside other cast members.\r\n\r\nGreg has had unique access to the sets of the Bond films from Casino Royale to No Time To Die, capturing cast and crew in a series of moments, ranging from the intimate to the spectacular. \r\n\r\nOf the prints, Greg Williams says: “I’m immensely proud to have have worked with Michael G. Wilson and Barbara Broccoli and be a guest on their incredible movie sets for over 20 years. During that time I have had the opportunity to document Daniel Craig’s remarkable journey as James Bond. From his original screen test through to the poster shoot on No Time to Die, these 25 photographs are some of my absolute favourites..\r\n\r\nDetails. In a choice of two sizes, this limited edition print is studio stamped for authenticity at Greg\'s Mayfair studio and ready to be framed. Archival pigment print on Hahnemühle Fine Art Baryta Satin 300gsm.\r\n\r\nSizes.\r\n10x12\" print in a limited edition of 500\r\n16x12\" print in a limited edition of 250\r\n                             \r\n            \r\n                             \r\n            ',350,'1697326202404.jpg',7),(44,'James Bond Canvas & Leather Duffel Bag - By Michael Kors Collection','Designed as part of the limited-edition MKC x 007 collaboration, the James Bond Canvas & Leather Duffel Bag by Michael Kors Collection is a weekend travel essential. Cotton canvas and supple calf leather combine for luxe effect, while an exclusive MKC x 007 luggage tag gives Bond-inspired style. Pack it for an overnight stay or weekend escape.\r\n\r\nDetails. Crafted in Italy, the Bond canvas & leather duffel has a timeless glamour with hand-rolled, edge-painted leather handles and angular gold metal hardware. Its luxe exterior is rendered in structured cotton canvas with smooth leather trims, while the interior has two pockets and is fully lined in a contrast suede. A detachable luggage tag on the exterior features the capsule’s MKC x 007 branding in contrast lettering, while a zip closure keeps things streamlined. Carry it over your shoulder for hands-free style, or detach the adjustable woven strap for a more refined look. the exterior is made up of 92% cotton, 8% polyurethane for a robust, durable finish.\r\n\r\nDimensions. W17\", H12\", D8.5\". Strap adjusts from 14.5\" to 21\"',900,'1697326406983.jpg',7),(45,'James Bond Quilted Down Jacket - By Bogner','Introducing the James Bond Quilted Down Performance Jacket by Bogner, part of the 007 60th anniversary collaboration with skiwear experts Bogner. This ultra-lightweight jacket is equally at home in the city and mountains and is finished with a slash of high-visibility red at the back. \r\n\r\nDetails. The high performance jacket is constructed with warmly padded quilting in a permanently water-repellant finish ripstop nylon technical fabric. Thermore® Ecodown® filling is made of recycled technical fibres and gives excellent thermal insulation. It has a high stand-up collar to protect from wind and cold, and a hood with a adjustable drawstring closure. The front features a concealed two-way zipper with wind-resistant front placket, and a bomber style ribbed hem for extra warmth and protection. Slant muffler pockets are closed with zips. The hood features contrast red lining, while the logo print on the left sleeve and ribbed cuffs complete the design.',595,'1697326849369.webp',2),(46,'James Bond 007 Spymaster Duo Fountain Pen - Numbered Edition - By Montegrappa','Introducing the James Bond 007 Spymaster Duo Fountain Pen by Montegrappa. Inspired by 007, this collectors\' edition writing instrument is fitting companion for any assignment. In the best traditions of James Bond gadgetry, the 007 Spymaster Duo has hidden secrets and is stylishly handmade from precious materials in a numbered edition of just 380 pieces. \r\n\r\nDetails.The pen is constructed from high-strength machined steel and aluminium. Its false upper barrel conceals a pair of special edition 007 cufflinks which can be\r\naccessed via a special locking mechanism and dummy blind cap. The pen has a reference-level 8mm nib in 18K gold, custom-engraved with the James Bond 60th Anniversary logo, and is engraved with its individual number on the steel grip.Features include the advanced Swift-Shot filling – an innovation which makes pioneering use of Montegrappa’s coveted Power-Push mechanism, The Swift-shot filling offers writers remote filling using high-capacity 007 \'bullet\' brass ink cartridges. A pair of cartridges is supplied together with an alloy/steel reloading pipette that uses Power-push hydraulic action to fill without spills. Filled cartridges are inserted into the writing block before reaffixing the barrel. \r\n\r\nThe pen features rifling on the cap and upper barrel which echoes the iconic, gun-barrel title sequence. The lower barrel is made of blackened alloy with a knurled, pistol-grip finish. Additional product markings include the 007 logo on the blind cap, cufflinks and a chevron pocket-clip, and the Bond family crest foil-stamped onto a companion journal. The pen and Swift-Shot accessories are housed in a custom travel case with secret compartments and a journal and two bottles of 007-branded ink.\r\n\r\nDimensions. L16.20cm, D1.85cm',4495,'1697327468196.webp',7);
